examples.en: We had many trials to go through.
Mock trials help students perfect their legal skills.
Early trials have shown that the treatment has some serious side effects.
The judge tried both father and son in separate trials.
In the experimental trials the amount of carbon was measured separately.
What couple can possibly foreknow the trials and tribulations that marriage will bring?
The drug has undergone extensive clinical trials (=tests to see if it is effective in treating people).
